<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>填写验证码</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/mui.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/app.css">
    <!--<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/setSecurityCode.css">-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/icon/iconfont.css">
</head>
<body>
<header class="mui-bar mui-bar-nav horbackground">
    <a class="mui-action-back mui-icon mui-icon-left-nav mui-pull-left"></a>
    <h1 class="mui-title whitecolor font18">设置手机号</h1>
</header>
<div class="mui-content">
    <ul class="margintop-20px" style="padding: 10px;">
        <li class="font14">
            <span class="maincolor">如需更改套餐</span>需要短信确认，验证码将发送手机宽带账户绑定手机<span id="phoneNum">180****2356</span>，请按提示操作。
        </li>
        <li class="margintop-10px font14">
            <input id="Code" type="number" class="font16" placeholder="请输入验证码" style="width: 60%;">
            <button id="getcode" type="button" class="mui-btn ridus5 horbackground mui-btn-outlined whitecolor float-right  btn30">
                获取验证码
            </button>
        </li>
        <li class="margintop-10px">
            <button id="submit" type="button" class="mui-btn ridus5 horbackground mui-btn-outlined whitecolor font16 btn">
                确定
            </button>
        </li>
        <div class="gray-8color font14 padding-10"><span class="maincolor">温馨提示：</span><br/>
            1、新套餐将在旧套餐到期日后方才生效。
        </div>

    </ul>
</div>
<script src="../js/mui.min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/template.js"></script>
<script src="../js/config.js"></script>
<!--<script src="../js/new/sendMessageCode.js"></script>-->
